wn.  \n\n---\n\n**Bottom line:** The cheapest fare you can grab today is **\u20b9\u202f4,328** for a one\u2011way Mumbai\u202f\u2192\u202fGoa flight. Book quickly to secure it!', type='TextMessage'), inner_messages=[]), 'name': 'Travel_Planner'}
